{"tid":2395301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貼文宣叫口號犯禁 教局國安指引叫學校篤學生灰：若嚴重請即報警","createTime":"2021-02-04T21:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:41:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6590da27b32a505495f76ce47de020525637139b","tid":2395301,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T21:10:07.000Z","msg":"教育局周四同時公佈有關國家安全的「學校具體措施」指引，要求學校今年8月底前向局方提交「檢視現行情況報告」及下學年工作計劃，並要每年遞交工作報告。文件要求學校，若有學生在校內佩戴具政治訊息飾物，或叫口號 、拉人鏈、貼文宣等，要視乎情況提醒學生或違反《港區國安法》等，遇到嚴重或緊急情況「請即報警」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/GKNQNSJ34FGADNPWR44QP3IYJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FGKNQNSJ34FGADNPWR44QP3IYJA%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=ca4425cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FGKNQNSJ34FGADNPWR44QP3IYJA%2F&h=abd9cc07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/GKNQNSJ34FGADNPWR44QP3IYJA/</a>"},{"pid":"c1af42aac134d18c6240681b8b95854c857a0d5e","tid":2395301,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T23:35:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a4d6d8f1170b309efe72f04381b2639842321746","tid":2395301,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T23:36:32.000Z","msg":"香港文革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5dcd264534626432f765d1c1c4df52f51ad6e2","tid":2395301,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"080a5168a3f694476b532918f489851f1d254ef0","tid":2395301,"uid":33206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"返校情節返返黎"}]}